languages.text: "Иногда твои речи напоминают предсказания наших провидцев, мон-кай. Весьма отдаленно, ибо едва ли ваши прорицатели могут сравниться с нашими".
"Your pronouncements sometimes remind me of our Farseers' prophecies, mon-keigh. Only vaguely, of course — your diviners are hardly comparable to ours."

languages.text: “你的宣言有时会让我想起我们先知的预言，猴子。当然，只是有那么一点点像而已，因为你们的占卜师很难与我们的占卜师相提并论。”
languages.original_text: "Your pronouncements sometimes remind me of our Farseers' prophecies, mon-keigh. Only vaguely, of course — your diviners are hardly comparable to ours."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: «Tus pronunciamientos me recuerdan en ocasiones a las profecías de nuestros videntes, mon-keigh. Solo de forma vaga, por supuesto; vuestros adivinos no pueden compararse con los nuestros».
languages.original_text: "Your pronouncements sometimes remind me of our Farseers' prophecies, mon-keigh. Only vaguely, of course — your diviners are hardly comparable to ours."

languages.text: 「お前の発言は、時折先見司の予言を思い起こさせるな、モン＝ケイ。もちろん、わずかばかりにているだけだが。お前たちの占い師は、我らのものとは比べ物にならん」
languages.original_text: "Your pronouncements sometimes remind me of our Farseers' prophecies, mon-keigh. Only vaguely, of course — your diviners are hardly comparable to ours."

traits.locale_text: 「お前の発言は、時折先見司の予言を思い起こさせるな、モン＝ケイ。もちろん、わずかばかりにているだけだが。お前たちの占い師は、我らのものとは比べ物にならん」
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Eure Verkündungen erinnern mich mitunter an die Prophezeiungen unserer Runenpropheten, Chem-Pan-Sey. Natürlich nur vage ... Eure Seher lassen sich mit den unseren nur schwer vergleichen."
languages.original_text: "Your pronouncements sometimes remind me of our Farseers' prophecies, mon-keigh. Only vaguely, of course — your diviners are hardly comparable to ours."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: « Vos paroles me rappellent vaguement les prophéties de nos Grands Prophètes, mon-keigh. Sauf que nos devins sont bien supérieurs aux vôtres. »

languages.text: "Açıklamaların bana bazen Ötesezenlerin kehanetlerini anımsatıyor mon-keigh. Yalnızca bir miktar ama tabii, sizin kâhinleriniz bizimkilerle kıyaslanamaz bile."
